{"tid":1759793,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"蔣麗芸(Ann姐)舉辦《投票問題申訴會》","createTime":"2019-11-28T00:21:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T00:25:25.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"935e46c78f759fce1f50cfa6d61bde09f4dded8d","tid":1759793,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:21:24.000Z","msg":"【投票問題申訴會】<br />\n<br />\n選舉前，建制派辦事處接連被縱火、入內搗亂及破壞，候選人擺街站時亦接二連三遭惡意搗亂、滋擾和破壞競選工作，支持者亦表達不敢去投票。<br />\n<br />\n投票日，「和你排」導致大排長龍，辛苦了長者並影響投票意欲；另外，不但用身份證副本可投票及有市民領取選票時發現已經「被投票」，更有不少市民指出有票站早上大排長龍時段的投票人數，跟黃昏幾乎沒有人排隊時段的累計投票人數卻差不多，引起大量質疑。<br />\n<br />\n投票完結後，點票過程為人詬病，候選人投訴點票場中站滿反對派支持者，建制支持者無法進入觀看，亦有出現覆檢廢票而建制候選人反勝的情況，事後引起大量對選舉公平性的質疑。<br />\n<br />\n選舉不公之聲此起彼落，有見及此，蔣麗芸議員(Ann姐)舉辦《投票問題申訴會》，誠意邀請你參加，分享您的意見！詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：11月29日（星期五）<br />\n時間：16:30-18:30<br />\n地點：金鐘立法會綜合大樓<br />\n截止報名：11月28日（星期四）15:00<br />\n<br />\n出席嘉賓: 政府官員(有待最後落實)<br />\n<br />\n如人數太多，將抽籤決定。成功獲邀人士，將於11月28日黃昏以電話訊息通知。<br />\n<br />\n報名方法：<br />\n1. Google form：<br />\n<a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc0FIaNfHWghWqt7Lf5Nb0jg1Lb4k1hgQw-3BruVS4U-5IGJg/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdocs.google.com%2Fforms%2Fd%2Fe%2F1FAIpQLSc0FIaNfHWghWqt7Lf5Nb0jg1Lb4k1hgQw-3BruVS4U-5IGJg%2Fviewform%3Fvc%3D0%26c%3D0%26w%3D1&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9Dcv4r%2BPR%2BKiJG6VnsQYGapQ%3D&h=8d5ecf3b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc0FIaNfHWghWqt7Lf5Nb0jg1Lb4k1hgQw-3BruVS4U-5IGJg/viewform?vc=0&amp;c=0&amp;w=1</a><br />\n<br />\n2. WhatsApp：<br />\n64413227 （請填上姓名、身份證首四個號碼、手提電話號碼）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c7s65WC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc7s65WC.jpg&h=73f887cb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c018a1d69a1b0e83260567ca9798483e2b5f42e","tid":1759793,"uid":263197,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:22:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f24f5bcfd01ec3f9564bbbd88622ee8091786e","tid":1759793,"uid":249263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:22:53.000Z","msg":"特朗普簽左法案啦！快啲多謝幫過手的議員啦！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1759783\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1759783</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"745f93475263f76e50ddc113bb7e4ae5cd35e838","tid":1759793,"uid":54433,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:23:12.000Z","msg":"咁好嘅活動必須積極參與"},{"pid":"b06d5cb4c0c90c92e82ebeb9e6bbabb6f3d0aee5","tid":1759793,"uid":93717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:23:29.000Z","msg":"包唔包海鮮餐？<br />\n上次個間麻麻"},{"pid":"b044e363f3f13ba79852e0a4e806c59d99d95ad1","tid":1759793,"uid":320680,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:25:08.000Z","msg":"咁我哋要去投訴 旅遊巴、福袋、利是、掌心雷<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cd99ce2c7dd00d0186b798842277c266f55fbdd","tid":1759793,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b06d5cb4c0c90c92e82ebeb9e6bbabb6f3d0aee5","tid":1759793,"uid":93717,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:23:29.000Z","msg":"包唔包海鮮餐？<br />\n上次個間麻麻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T00:25:25.000Z","msg":"包"}]}